# STREAMING::IS_MODEL_A_VEHICLE

## Summary
Returns TRUE if this model is a vehicle

## Parameters
* **MODEL_NAMES** modelHashKey

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether the specified model represents a vehicle.
